<HEADLINE> Chinese Banker Honored in London </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, December 3 (Xinhua) -- Wu Kung-Chao, a veteran Chinese
banker, was awarded an honorary degree of Doctor of Philosophy by
London Guildhall University today for his contribution to
international and, especially, Sino-British banking relations.
</P>
<P>
