<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, December 4 (Xinhua) -- Information technology (IT)
exhibition "Comdex'96" opened here today with over 30,000 IT
products on display.
</P>
<P>
The products include hardware and software as well as
electronic components, etc. and more than 500 corporates both
domestic and foreign participated in the exhibition. Among them
are world-famous IT companies like Microsoft, Siemens, Nixdorf
Information Systems, 3 Com, Intel Corp., Samsung and Polaroid.
</P>
