<HEADLINE> Largest Automobile Stereo System Enterprise Operational </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NANJING, December 4 (Xinhua) -- China's largest automobile
stereo system manufacturer, the Jiangsu Donghua Electronics
Company, has gone into operation in this capital of east China's
Jiangsu Province.
</P>
<P>
With an investment of 26 million HK dollars in the first-phase
construction, the company was jointly set up and is run by the
Jiangsu Technology Import &AMP; Export Corporation and the Donghua
Electronics Co. Ltd. of Hong Kong
</P>
<P>
The company has an annual production capacity of two million
items of 10 series for both Chinese and foreign customers.
</P>
<P>
A large percentage of its products will be exported to Britain,
France, Germany and the Middle East, with expected export earnings
of 100 million US dollars per year.
</P>
<P>
In addition, it will manufacture high-grade stereo systems for
a number of leading automobile stereo manufacturers in Germany and
Japan. 
</P>
